                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Your service in one project is independent of the services rendered in any other projects, since the funding agency and pay are different.
                            This temporary engagement in this project or in any other project will not confer you any title to permanent employment at the Centre.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Your services may be discontinued at any point of time <b>
