                            <ol type="a">
                                <li>
                                    Self-attested copy of S.S.L.C. or School Certificate in proof of the date of birth.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Self-attested copy of Certificates relating to all your educational and technical qualifications and previous experience, if any.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Self-attested copy of address Proof and Pan card.
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Also You have to submit the following documents at the time of Verification:
                            <ol type="a">
                                <li>
                                    Attestation (form enclosed)
                                </li>
                                @*<li>
                                        A declaration that you are not under bond or agreement under obligation to serve the
                                        Central / state Government / University or a public Authority / Undertaking
                                        Institution / Autonomous body.
                                    </li>*@
                                @*<li>
                                        Relief Certificate from your present employer, if any
                                    </li>*@
                                <li>
                                    An undertaking assigning all rights in respect of investigations and to abide by the
                                    rules and regulations of the Centre for Industrial Consultancy & Sponsored Research
                                    (as per form enclosed). Along with the declaration that you are not under bond or agreement
                                    or under obligation to serve the Central / state Government / University or a public Authority / Undertaking /Institution / Autonomous body.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    If belonging to SC/ST category, submit the certificate issued by a competent authority. This offer is provisional and is subject to the verification
